{"tid":1482143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"818前最後文宣 大家幫手散出去","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:00:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:49:57.000Z","uid":241349,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8c1836709aaa68e4baf7e990dbc8c2094abe8bc7","tid":1482143,"uid":241349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"大家已經一齊走過兩個幾月<br />\n唔好再重踏雨運既命運<br />\n我地宜家已經唔可以再輸<br />\n一輸就輸晒幾代人<br />\n到時中共會全力打壓香港人自由<br />\n818 今日一定要走出黎<br />\n發生咩事都好<br />\n我地都要堅持住不割蓆！不指責！不篤灰！<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家頂住啊！<br />\n要相信有朝一日 煲底除罩再聚</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">WE ARE ONE</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人  一條心<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZAYG7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZAYG7Q.jpg&h=bbad84f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVXL6zq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVXL6zq.jpg&h=dab9e2c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vrhder.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vrhder.jpg&h=48c4326f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oc2L6zs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foc2L6zs.jpg&h=3a313763&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ip6w17N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fip6w17N.jpg&h=10baf863&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ftxoTet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FftxoTet.jpg&h=34978e12&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EPzq6zu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEPzq6zu.jpg&h=8c2fda53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73e2dde80c82c01dd35e74f9e980d01f9e6ced39","tid":1482143,"uid":241349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:03:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c684e5bc5fac33b857b618693d74ff0373b4b9","tid":1482143,"uid":241349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aaaa267d6ac8b82b43f8d9b19240172c1c95852","tid":1482143,"uid":241349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed23d1a7b230c45f0ff900054e061cf9a02e6fb","tid":1482143,"uid":241349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7748f782d10bc9658622069d740c6aaf72173b","tid":1482143,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8eed0dfbf9eb8b7c842c07de74884685408d33cb","tid":1482143,"uid":241349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:22:37.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa4b289f9afcbc1fc2fe133aff7161b0541227d","tid":1482143,"uid":24